Default chat style for this repo:

- Keep assistant messages extremely concise.
- Do not report routine changed files.
- Do not paste code diffs or large snippets unless explicitly asked.
- Never show file code diffs in chat unless the user explicitly asks for a diff.
- Prefer silent work over progress narration for small tasks.
- Final replies should be one short sentence unless there is a blocker.
- Assume the user will inspect detailed diffs with Git.
